---

<Layout title="Alexandre Izanic | Portfolio">
  <main
    class="bg-white max-w-7xl px-5 md:px-20 m-auto my-14 flex flex-col gap-6"
  >
    <section class="flex flex-col gap-2">
      <div class="p-4 rounded-lg border flex flex-col gap-2">
        <div class="flex gap-5 items-end">
          <div class="font-bold text-4xl text-center">Hey, I'm Alex</div>
          <div class="flex gap-2 justify-center items-center">
            <button
              class="px-4 py-1 h-fit bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 border-gray-400 border rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-black/90 hover:bg-gray-200 transition duration-300 ease-in-out text-sm"
            >
              <a
                href="https://calendly.com/alexandre-izanic/meet"
                target="_blank"
              >
                Schedule a call
              </a>
            </button>
            <a
              href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/alexandre-izanic/"
              target="_blank"
            >
              <div
                class="border rounded-lg w-auto flex justify-center items-center hover:bg-slate-100 p-1"
              >
                <img src={LinkedInLogo.src} class="h-auto w-6" />
              </div>
            </a>

            <a href="https://github.com/AlexandreIzanic" target="_blank">
              <div
                class="border rounded-lg w-auto flex justify-center items-center hover:bg-slate-100 p-2 h-full"
              >
                <img src={GithubLogo.src} class="h-auto w-4" />
              </div>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="font-medium text-sm text-left text-gray-800">
          I'm a freelance <span class="font-bold">FullStack developer</span>, <br
          />
          Specializing in building professional user interfaces and complex applications
          with a<span class="font-bold"> user-centric</span> approach.
        </p>
      </div>

      <CardPrimary
        title="Askform"
        role="Cofounder & Fullstack Developer"
        tags={[
          "React",
          "Typescript",
          "Supabase",
          "Zod",
          "Node",
          "Stripe",
          "Zustand",
          "Vitest",
          "Astro",
          "Github Actions",
          "Vercel",
          "Redis",
          "Strapi",
          "Plausible",
        ]}
        link="https://askform.fr"
      >
        <div slot="body" class="font-semibold">
          Development of Askform, a platform that allows companies to <span
            class="font-bold">centralize</span
          >
          and simplify <span class="font-bold"
            >request management workflows.</span
          >
        </div>
        <div slot="description" class="font-medium text-gray-400 ml-4 mb-2">
          • Workspaces to centralize customer requests and configure <span
            class="underline">workflows related to actions or team members</span
          >
          <br />• <span class="underline">Performance analytics</span> for teams
          members and individual forms
        </div>
      </CardPrimary>

