    </section>

    <section class="flex flex-col gap-5">
      <CardUpmail
        title="Upmail"
        img=""
        role="Freelance Fullstack Developer"
        tags={[
          "React",
          "Typescript",
          "Langchain",
          "Mistral API",
          "OpenAI API",
          "Node",
          "Supabase",
          "Zod",
          "Vercel",
        ]}
      >
        <div slot="body" class="font-semibold">
          Development of an AI-boosted email client for professionals
        </div>
        <div slot="description" class="font-medium text-gray-400 ml-4 mb-2">
          • AI agent integration
          <span class="underline">Langchain(Mistral AI API)</span> to categorize
          emails
          <br />
          • <span class="underline">AI draft writing </span> with the possibility
          of schedule the sending
          <br />
          • Workflow trigger by new email with<span class="underline"
            >Gmail API</span
          > and <span class="underline">GCP PUB / SUB</span>
        </div></CardUpmail
      >
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <Card
          title="Le Stud - Startup Studio"
          img={FinotorBg.src}
          body="The only all-in-one solution to manage your business accounting, finances and bank accounts"
          role="Freelance Fullstack Developer"
          tags={[
            "React",
            "Node",
            "PostgreSQL",
            "Sequelize",
            "Stripe",
            "Mixpanel",
            "i18n",
            "Joi",
          ]}
        >
          <div slot="body" class="font-semibold">
            As a developer in a team, I contributed to the development of a
            platform for managing accounting.
          </div>
          <div slot="description" class="font-medium text-gray-400 ml-4 mb-2">
            • Implementation of data <span class="underline">migration</span> management
            from existing platforms like <span class="underline">Xero</span>
            <br />
            • <span class="underline">User-centric</span> development with a strong
            <span class="underline">UX</span> approach around the product
            <br />
            • Key player in laying the foundations of an <span class="underline"
              >early-stage startup</span
            >
          </div>
        </Card>

        <Card
          title="ViaTransit"
