            MaaS solutions that adapt to all needs and network sizes
          </div>
          <div slot="description" class="font-medium text-gray-400 ml-4 mb-2">
            • Refactoring of <span class="underline">spaghetti code</span> into a
            cleaner and more maintainable structure <br /> • Migration of the authentication
            system from <span class="underline">Firebase</span>
            to
            <span class="underline">Supabase</span>
            <br />
            • Migration from Next Pages router to <span class="underline"
              >App router</span
            >
          </div>
        </Card>

